    <div id="conTit">
     <h1>武汉市民宗委原主任王献良因感染新型冠状病毒去世
      
                       <em class="icon_key"></em>
                 
                   
 
    </h1>
     <!--baidu begin-->
     <div class="bd_block" style="display:none"><span class="bd_block" id="pubtime_baidu">2020-01-26 23:49:06</span><span class="bd_block" id="source_baidu">来源： <a href="https://china.caixin.com/2020-01-26/101508637.html" target="_blank">财新网</a></span><span class="bd_block" id="author_baidu">作者：覃建行</span><span class="bd_block" id="editor_baidu">责任编辑：陈宝成</span></div>
     <!--baidu end-->
     <div class="artInfo" id="artInfo">
      
      2020年01月26日 23:49
      
      来源于
      <a href=http://www.caixin.com target=_blank>财新网</a>
      
      
      
